                  <p class="lead">
                    Welcome to our poster webshop, where we have an extensive
                    collection of posters to cater to every taste and style.
                    Whether you're looking to decorate your home, office, or any
                    other space, we have a vast selection of posters that are
                    perfect for you. Our posters are printed on high-quality
                    paper and are available in different sizes to fit your
                    needs. From motivational quotes and landscapes to abstract
                    art and movie posters, we have it all. We also offer fast
                    and reliable shipping so you can receive your posters in no
                    time. Browse through our collection today and find the
                    perfect posters to enhance your space.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="row pt-4">
            
                <!--Function that generate cards and fills it with everything in our data.json file-->
                <% Object.keys(Posters).forEach((poster) => { %>
                <div class="card border-0 bg-transparent" style="width: 18rem">
                  <a href="/Product/<%= poster %>"
                    ><img
                      src="<%= Posters[poster].img %>"
                      class="card-img-top"
                      alt="..."
                  /></a>
                  <div class="card-body bg-transparent">
                    <h6 class="card-title my-0">
                      <a href="/Product/<%= poster %>" id="link-text"
                        ><%= Posters[poster].artist %></a
                      >
                    </h6>
                    <p class="card-text">
                      <a href="/Product/<%= poster %>" id="link-text"
                        ><%= Posters[poster].title %></a
                      >
                    </p>
                    <p class="card-text">
                      <a href="/Product/<%= poster %>" id="price-text"
                        ><%= Posters[poster].price %>,00 kr</a
                      >
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <% }); %>
